reviews_data.review_text: I absolutely had the best time here! The ambiance and decor was amazing I could spend the whole day there for that alone. Their coffee was delicious and tastec amazing. I had haraz latte and Harazi Mufawar and am actually obsessed with both. The cakes were all sooo moist and flavorful. You can tell that the quality here is very high. Everyone was friendly also, I can't wait to ga back!
Got the mocha frappe and it was soooo good 🙌🏽 perfectly blended and not too sweet. Service was fast and everyone was super friendly. Definitely coming back!! 😍
Amazing service, the Iced pistachio latte was not overpoweringly sweet, thank you!
Amazing place to study or chat with friends and family. There's a wide variety of drinks and desserts, definitely a great location!
Best location I’ve tried! Great spot!
Haraz Coffee in University City is a great spot to study and meet with friends. It has a beautiful interior and the staff are great. Not to mention the owners are hospitable and kind!!
Great coffee. Love the interior!
Haraz Coffee at Charlotte University is amazing—great atmosphere, high-quality coffee, and super friendly staff. Perfect spot to study or hang out. Highly recommend!

Absolutely love this coffee shop! The atmosphere is cozy and welcoming, and the staff is always friendly and attentive. The matcha is AMAZING smooth, flavorful, and perfectly made. If you’re a matcha lover, this place is a must. Highly recommend and will definitely be coming back!
Haraz Coffee at University is a solid spot. Great coffee, fresh pastries, and a friendly, relaxed vibe inside.
Great customer service amazing drinks and desserts beats every other haraz in the area 100%

Whether you’re studying, catching up with friends, or enjoying a quiet moment with a cup of coffee, the view and ambiance make it a comfortable escape from the busy campus energy.
